name: My first interactive OBJKT
description:
This is my first interactive OBJKT in HEN.
Please consider following my twitter account to be a part of this incredible start.

Like me, maybe you would love to start discovering the potential of this new way of creating art on the blockchain.

I invite you to learn together. Go to my facebook page if you like: @wikibuda (https://www.facebook.com/wikibuda). There I will start sharing this exciting trip.

The first video I will post on Facebook will teach you how to upload your first interactive NFT, just like the one you see on the screen.

Happy # OBJKT4OBJKT, that is HAPPY # OBJKT4OBJp5.js

Greetings Vincent_NFT aka Wikibuda.


HOW TO: just touch the screen with the mouse or your touch-screen monitor and scroll width and length without releasing.
